</omgroup>

<omgroup xml:id="fol">
 <metadata><dc:title>First-Order Logics</dc:title></metadata>
 <omtext xml:id="fol-intro">
  <CMP>
   First-order logics are logics that allow quantification over individuals. They
   are usually untyped.
  </CMP>
 </omtext>

